{{! Human-verification field. Receives the page content as context. In
    production the live Cloudflare Turnstile widget renders; on dev and staging
    the adapter is stubbed and no real challenge exists, so a labeled card
    stands in its place to make the bypass obvious to anyone testing. }}
{{#if turnstileSiteKey}}
  <div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="{{turnstileSiteKey}}"></div>
{{else if captchaStubbed}}
  <div class="card card-static mb-4">
    <p class="card-title">You are human</p>
    <p class="text-muted fs-sm m-0">Developer stub: the live Cloudflare Turnstile challenge is bypassed in this environment. Production shows the real challenge here.</p>
  </div>
{{/if}}
